data.description: Have you been dreaming about your next "fixer-upper" in Milton but just haven't found the right house? Well, look no more! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on a large 1/3 of an acre lot with a pool and a large dog run. Located right off Berryhill Rd you are 5 minutes from a hospital and George Stone Vocational. 10 Minutes to Publix, High School, middle school, and elementary school. Close to shopping, restaurants, and much more. With the base being so close this could be a great rental or for someone who wants to put some sweat equity into their home. With a little TLC, you could make this house your home.
